        <h3>Why is SEO pricing in Leeds cheaper than London?</h3>
        <p>Leeds SEO agencies operate with significantly lower overheads than London firms. Office costs, salaries, and operational expenses are 30-50% lower in Leeds compared to central London. This does not mean lower quality. Many Leeds SEO professionals have worked at London agencies and bring the same expertise at more competitive rates. You get London-calibre strategy without the London price tag.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>Are there long-term contracts?</h3>
        <p>We require a minimum three-month commitment because SEO results take time to materialise. After the initial three months, our agreements roll month-to-month with 30 days notice to cancel. We do not lock clients into 12-month contracts because we believe our results should earn your continued business, not a contract clause.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>What is not included in the monthly price?</h3>
