      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>How quickly will I see results from SEO?</h3>
        <p>Most Leeds businesses see measurable improvements within 3-6 months. Technical fixes and local SEO optimisations often produce results within weeks. Content-driven and link-building strategies take longer to compound. We set realistic expectations during the discovery call and provide monthly progress reports so you can track improvements against your baseline.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
